It has been suggested, Stephen, that maybe this is a whistleblower suggestion by the defense, but we live in the Victorian age.

10:28.921 --> 10:29.642
Oh?

10:30.423 --> 10:32.025
Yeah.

10:32.045 --> 10:33.648
Do you think that's a preposterous suggestion?

10:33.728 --> 10:35.510
It would have been a better age to live.

10:35.610 --> 10:37.974
