It's so hard to find parts.

12:20.054 --> 12:26.944
Yeah, I pretty much do.

12:26.965 --> 12:29.869
Now, you know, there was a, were you ever interested, like, in the Gronier 100?

12:29.929 --> 12:31.371
Oh, yeah, yeah.

12:31.692 --> 12:33.975
I had that bibliography, and I had a,

12:34.613 --> 12:35.874
