13:52.520 --> 13:53.662
Is that true?

13:53.762 --> 13:54.263
Yeah, yeah.

13:54.283 --> 14:01.033
Well, and all of it, you know, not only the books, but the doorknobs and the windows and the old house and even the people, Mr. Hall.

14:01.435 --> 14:04.159
Adam today has been exposed to.

