So you went up to Dartmouth, too?

14:54.753 --> 14:55.053
That's amazing.

14:55.073 --> 14:56.254
You went everywhere up to Hanover.

14:56.334 --> 15:01.260
You know, I've never been up to Hanover, New Hampshire, but I've lived in New England all my life.

15:02.084 --> 15:04.967
Because that's the way the heck up there, Hadover is.

